        },
        "subject": "LU-2145 server: move mgs ptlrpc service to the unified server",
        "message": "LU-2145 server: move mgs ptlrpc service to the unified server\n\nMove ptlrpc service creation from mgs to the unified server.\nMGS register just slice of opcode handlers upon initialization. This\nis first step to moving request handling there too and unify it.\n\nNote: mgs handlers are set to NULL in this patch and mgs_handle is\nstill called instead, this is temporary just to split patches into\nsmall parts\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <tappro@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I43ac0c88c935f1504a52baa2ae1236384f548ddf\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
